{"tid":804388,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[有片]美國有條友用左幾年整左隻恐怖驚出黎 氣氛好撚柒正","createTime":"2018-09-03T03:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T19:51:42.000Z","uid":66943,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d229cac60d07f3c19b878ad83c024635b93c04ae","tid":804388,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T03:38:37.000Z","msg":"美國洛杉磯的遊戲開發者Ryan Schake最近成立了個人遊戲工作室Transient Light Studio，並曝光了他一個人開發的FPS恐怖遊戲《Dark Vale》，該作採用最新版CryEngine 5引擎開發，畫面令人驚嘆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/113458_341660228c4a8dee4864f277308e49cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F113458_341660228c4a8dee4864f277308e49cc.jpg&h=74812d23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這款遊戲由Ryan Schake耗費數年開發，集結了不同風格，比如荒地、夏季雨林、神秘地下戰爭掩體，恐怖洞穴，還融合了多種題材，比如科幻、現代建築、柴油朋克，所有這些都已完成關卡製作，並且直接來自遊戲內截圖。<br />\n<br />\n　根據Ryan Schake曝光的信息，這款遊戲設定為1960年代，涉及戰爭監禁、冷戰間諜行動，還出現了鬧鬼的醫院，以及地獄之門這種超自然力量。<br />\n<br />\n　　不過Ryan Schake並未表示什麼時候發佈，但目前這些環境截圖與演示已經是完成的版本，至於NPC與劇情並未展示詳情，期待遊戲正式上架發售。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Le5SrLDxrGg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLe5SrLDxrGg&d=hK15R4YwuR0BgyllpPyoOmMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=2f674782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Le5SrLDxrGg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TmyOMwfJltQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTmyOMwfJltQ&d=hK15R4YwuR0BgyllpPyoOmMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=d19626c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TmyOMwfJltQ</a>"},{"pid":"ab25083d77a923e3b38f0af66a5fbfab0c2a7f6b","tid":804388,"uid":58140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T03:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好高汁"},{"pid":"2f58442281418ed7342c003554171d2